<figureCitation id="132D06C7B001D778A2669066FD48746C" box="[597,659,1538,1560]" captionStart="Figs 20–21" captionStartId="18.[166,205,1098,1120]" captionTargetBox="[218,1177,182,1002]" captionTargetId="figure-310@18.[205,1193,174,1012]" captionText="Figs 20–21.Xerophilomyia nigropicta Rohd. 20 (male):a — habitus in lateral view; b — head in profile; c — head in frontal view; d — head in dorsal view; e — widdle leg in antrerior view; f — wing; g — abdomen in dorsal view; h — label. 21 (female): a —habitus in lateral view; b — abdomen in dorsal view; c — head in profile; d — head in frontal view; e — head in dorsal view; f — wing abdomen, lateral view; g — label." pageId="15" pageNumber="198">fig. 20</figureCitation>
