<superScript id="7C63B70AB001D778A36B9065FCBF7476" attach="left" box="[856,868,1537,1549]" fontSize="5" pageId="15" pageNumber="198">rd</superScript>
abdominal tergite separated from lateral ones by broad stripes of dusting; pattern of abdomen black (
